Our story







                        History
                    
From start-up to global business



It all began in South Africa in 1991. We were a small start-up offering domestic strategies in an emerging market. Now we’re an international business managing approximately $124 billion* for clients based all over the world.
*As at 30.06.17













                        Perspective
                    
Unique journey: unique insight



We are on a truly unique journey. Launched in South Africa in 1991, we are one of the first asset management firms to build a global franchise from emerging market origins. This means we see the world differently, allowing our clients to benefit from our unique insight.













                        People
                    
More than a job



We are curious for our clients. We put our clients and our people at the centre of our business. This is after all their business. Our people enjoy working without constraints and they’re passionate about what they do. That’s why so many of our senior people have been with us for so long.













