Company


A Better Future for Surplus







								Company
							
A Better Future for Surplus




















One Company. Triple Bottom Line.

When it comes to surplus asset management, Liquidity Services is the pioneer of progress. We’re committed to intelligently capturing the enduring value of surplus assets, benefiting our clients, our buyers, and our planet. By managing assets across the globe more profitably, more efficiently, and more strategically, we build a better future for your surplus.


                                                Contact Us
                                            




















Discover the Story of Surplus






 


















About Us


 

Services


        We offer consultative surplus asset management, valuation, and sales solutions that maximize total supply chain value.
    



 

Locations


        With nearly 50 locations worldwide, Liquidity Services provides clients with global coverage for their surplus needs.
    



 

History


        Guided by our innovative approach to the reverse supply chain, we’ve evolved into the industry leader we are today.
    



 

Core Values


        Our core values laid the foundation for our growth and enable our continued success. We remain true to them today.
    



 

Management


        Our experienced leadership team drives innovation, efficiency, and excellence in every aspect of our organization.
    






















Industries We Serve
Liquidity Services provides organizations in every major industry with solutions tailored to address their most important needs.





