A Better Future for Surplus







								Marketplaces
							
Bullseye! More Targeted Buyers for Your Surplus.










Explore Liquidity Services’ Surplus Asset Marketplaces
Our surplus asset marketplaces are segmented by industry, from energy to retail, allowing you to reach the most targeted buyers for your surplus. With 3 million buyers throughout the globe and nearly $7 billion in completed transactions for clients, Liquidity Services provides the world's largest marketplace for surplus across all asset categories and conditions.




Capital Assets



 
Surplus industrial assets in over 500 categories and a wide range of industries, from aerospace & defense to fast-moving consumer goods


 
Surplus oil, gas, petrochemical, utilities, and mining equipment and supplies


 
Surplus assets from various commercial entities


 
New value-priced and premium construction equipment from proven brands as well as qualified new-to-market brands






Retail Assets



 
Surplus and returned inventory from retailers, consumer brand manufacturers, and wholesale outlets in pallet quantities


 
Surplus and returned inventory from retailers, consumer brand manufacturers, and wholesale outlets in truckload quantities


 
Surplus, returned, and refurbished inventory from retailers, consumer brand manufacturers, and wholesale outlets for consumers






Government Assets



 
Surplus and scrap assets from the U.S. Government's Department of Defense


 
Surplus and confiscated items primarily from state and local U.S. government agencies


 
Surplus assets from the U.S. Government's Department of Defense for consumer purchases



























